{"tid":792551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]喺元朗俾人打","createTime":"2018-08-24T15:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T17:33:50.000Z","uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4821b8718f12a0c050f587976b7ff83e5db38bdb","tid":792551,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:37:59.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟夜晩行行下有啲尿急，想上樓問人借個廁所<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上到樓，禁個門鐘，嘩，我屌吖，啲姐姐又着到幾性感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我用廣東話，問佢得唔得入去，佢都幾熱情，笑住咁歡迎我<br />\n<br />\n我尿急，入去屙咗個尿就走，一落樓俾幾條Mk 仔打，屌佢老尾，有腹肌，打撚到我仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一個仲口噏噏咁話走數<br />\n<br />\n我心諗佢都痴撚線<br />\n<br />\n我究竟做錯乜先俾人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00762d5cba95ac3e48d1d66bc401b6eb4d238b6b","tid":792551,"uid":154759,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:40:39.000Z","msg":"冇沖廁？"},{"pid":"46463f9d53566943db7d69a4e6e92ceafcd52151","tid":792551,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:43:17.000Z","msg":"巴打快啲cut返個腹肌出嚟同佢地再戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951155f71e007f6d1f96aaa4f1b7d0a640f91634","tid":792551,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:43:52.000Z","msg":"屎都瀨埋"},{"pid":"59013f46ffb7fafc87dd7061f4e0f1e2220ffa8d","tid":792551,"uid":199139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"打返佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcffa7a24d30b7213c47ff06ce5e0219cf80486b","tid":792551,"uid":136760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:44:52.000Z","msg":"係咪冇放返低塊廁板呀？"},{"pid":"07ca7c06f5b95a90e483d86f4131353539ec2972","tid":792551,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47475530b39e9a9c6dbac37cd5000c8df9e5310","tid":792551,"uid":30389,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:57:13.000Z","msg":"Mk仔大叫：「有廁客！」"},{"pid":"8b3eaf06be106c2f89d8eb34ff5a6dea2bfec900","tid":792551,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"00762d5cba95ac3e48d1d66bc401b6eb4d238b6b","tid":792551,"uid":154759,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:40:39.000Z","msg":"冇沖廁？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T17:21:14.000Z","msg":"好似真係冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eeb46248c6ee634df85a82a17f1ba795554fffe","tid":792551,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"46463f9d53566943db7d69a4e6e92ceafcd52151","tid":792551,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:43:17.000Z","msg":"巴打快啲cut返個腹肌出嚟同佢地再戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T17:22:21.000Z","msg":"我已經好大聲屌柒同打鳩佢，<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">係心入面</span>"},{"pid":"0532ca7302b4c6101a09afff573f4714443fae0e","tid":792551,"uid":187076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T17:22:55.000Z","msg":"支持樓主一打十"},{"pid":"eb3b47570ef1cb4b88b78340b569b4e937ec8daf","tid":792551,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fcffa7a24d30b7213c47ff06ce5e0219cf80486b","tid":792551,"uid":136760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:44:52.000Z","msg":"係咪冇放返低塊廁板呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T17:22:59.000Z","msg":"無，但我有微笑講唔該哂"},{"pid":"3b20cab458c8ef343cf3cf079e434c15b2c54207","tid":792551,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0532ca7302b4c6101a09afff573f4714443fae0e","tid":792551,"uid":187076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T17:22:55.000Z","msg":"支持樓主一打十"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T17:31:51.000Z","msg":"我已經做緊尼馬，碌咗廿個圈都嚟<br />\n<br />\n不過一路碌圈，我一路係腦度拆解緊佢地嘅動作，同打返佢地轉路<br />\n<br />\n佢一個直拳，我一個鐘擺式避開，再加一個上勾拳落肚，之後一腳後踢腳，踢中後面雞心，再嚟一招金雞獨立，又兩件，剎那間再用寒冰掌，又推甩兩件，馬上再接掃堂腳，即刻冧低四個<br />\n<br />\n再拍拍雙手，揮一揮衣袖，頭也不回吹住口哨咁走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6762a8a175f8641f8efb95e4d8fd85e451bcd1a3","tid":792551,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"951155f71e007f6d1f96aaa4f1b7d0a640f91634","tid":792551,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:43:52.000Z","msg":"屎都瀨埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T17:32:24.000Z","msg":"唔屎急"},{"pid":"8d238d43a40fd2a06e5fb0cdaaff219ba414f435","tid":792551,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f47475530b39e9a9c6dbac37cd5000c8df9e5310","tid":792551,"uid":30389,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:57:13.000Z","msg":"Mk仔大叫：「有廁客！」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T17:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d3325f584db04955ac884e60b1978a1f394055","tid":792551,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"07ca7c06f5b95a90e483d86f4131353539ec2972","tid":792551,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T17:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512970b7cb9a7841fc9d3ab9c8e9095e6c0975e8","tid":792551,"uid":146917,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f47475530b39e9a9c6dbac37cd5000c8df9e5310","tid":792551,"uid":30389,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":